Q.L:
Minc'd Pies in Van, and Calves Heads in the Rear;
Alluding to the Mince Pies in Use about Christmass or New-year's Day, and to an inhuman Insult offered, or said to have been usually offered by a certain Party on the 31st of this Month (a Day-Nigro carbone notandus) to the Memory of the unhappy Charles.
It is unnecessary to observe here, that it is equally mean and cowardly to pluck a dead Lion by the Beard!
